offset_bottom = 687.0
bbcode_enabled = true
text = "The [i]Saint of Dusk?[/i]

She's praying for the next Elven Messiah--the one who purifies the Leyline, freeing it from Demons ...
and making its power wholly unusable by human hands.

Sun Temple's Generators will stop, the prophecy says, and with them, the machines of conquest and war.

The Age of Humanity will end."

